<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>FirmNest Group — AI-Powered Finance & Operations Advisory</title>
  <meta name="description" content="FirmNest Group brings AI-powered finance and operations advisory to founder-led and growth-stage businesses." />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Figtree:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --navy: #0F1F3D; --navy-hover: #1A3160;
      --blue: #2352C8; --blue-light: #EEF2FC;
      --slate: #4A5568; --slate-light: #8896A8;
      --bg: #F8F8F6; --white: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #E4E4DF; --border-dark: #CACAC2;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }

    /* A11y focus */
    a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible, input:focus-visible, textarea:focus-visible, select:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--blue);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* Nav */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 60px;
      height: 66px;
      background: rgba(248,248,246,0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: box-shadow .3s;
    }
    nav.scrolled { box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(15,31,61,.07); }

    .nav-logo img { height: 34px; display: block; object-fit: contain; }

    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--slate);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--navy); }

    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 9px 22px;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--navy-hover); }

    /* Sections */
    section { padding: 72px 60px; scroll-margin-top: 90px; }
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--blue);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 3.5vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.12;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
    }
    h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }
    .lead {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--slate);
      max-width: 520px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* Hero */
    #hero {
      min-height: 88vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 110px;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #E0E0DA 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      opacity: .5;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 740px; padding: 0 60px; }

    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--blue);
      border: 1px solid rgba(35,82,200,.2);
      background: var(--blue-light);
      padding: 7px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }
    .hero-tag-dot {
      width: 5px; height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--blue);
      animation: blink 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.25} }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 68px);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--slate);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 34px;
      transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--navy-hover); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 48px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg);
      width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    }
    .hs {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      max-width: 220px;
    }
    .hs:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .hs-val {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .hs-val span { color: var(--blue); }
    .hs-lbl {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--slate-light);
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }

    /* Services */
    #services { background: var(--bg); }
    .section-header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--border);
      gap: 1px;
    }
    .svc {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 30px 26px;
      position: relative;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .svc:hover { background: #FDFCFB; }
    .svc:hover .svc-arr { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    .svc-n {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      color: var(--blue);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .svc-title {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .svc-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--slate);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .svc-arr {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 26px;
      right: 26px;
      color: var(--blue);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-5px);
      transition: opacity .2s, transform .2s;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .svc.ai-card {
      background: var(--blue-light);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .svc.ai-card .svc-title { color: var(--blue); }
    .svc.ai-card .svc-desc { color: rgba(35,82,200,.6); }

    /* How */
    #how { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); }
    #how h2 { color: var(--white); }
    #how h2 em { color: #7AA3F5; }
    #how .eyebrow { color: #7AA3F5; }

    .how-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    }
    .step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .step-n {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      color: #7AA3F5;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding-top: 2px;
      width: 20px;
    }
    .step-title {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .step-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .how-panel { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); padding: 26px; }
    .panel-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .panel-bars { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 5px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .pb {
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      border-top: 2px solid rgba(122,163,245,.4);
      transform: scaleY(0);
      transform-origin: bottom;
      animation: riseB 1s ease-out forwards;
    }
    @keyframes riseB { to { transform: scaleY(1); } }
    .pb:nth-child(1){height:38%;animation-delay:.05s} .pb:nth-child(2){height:55%;animation-delay:.10s}
    .pb:nth-child(3){height:42%;animation-delay:.15s} .pb:nth-child(4){height:68%;animation-delay:.20s}
    .pb:nth-child(5){height:58%;animation-delay:.25s} .pb:nth-child(6){height:82%;animation-delay:.30s;background:rgba(122,163,245,.1);border-color:#7AA3F5}
    .pb:nth-child(7){height:74%;animation-delay:.35s} .pb:nth-child(8){height:94%;animation-delay:.40s;background:rgba(122,163,245,.1);border-color:#7AA3F5}

    .panel-blabel { font-size: 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.18); letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .panel-metrics { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
    .pm { padding: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.02); }
    .pm-val { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 20px; color: #7AA3F5; font-weight: 400; }
    .pm-lbl { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.22); margin-top: 3px; }

    /* Clients */
    #clients { background: var(--white); }
    .clients-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 36px;
    }
    .cc { background: var(--white); padding: 24px 20px; transition: background .2s; }
    .cc:hover { background: var(--bg); }
    .cc-icon { font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cc-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .cc-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; }

    /* Why */
    #why { background: var(--bg); }
    .why-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      gap: 56px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .why-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .wp {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 16px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .wp:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .wp-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--blue);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .wp-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .wp-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }

    .why-callout {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 32px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 82px;
    }
    .wc-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .wc-quote {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: clamp(17px, 1.8vw, 21px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .wc-quote em { color: #7AA3F5; font-style: italic; }
    .wc-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: #7AA3F5;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .wc-btn:hover { background: #91B3F7; }

    /* Consultation */
    #consultation { background: var(--white); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .form-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .fi h3 {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
      font-size: 21px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .fi p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--slate);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .crow { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 11px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .cicon {
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--blue-light);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .ctext { font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.45; }
    .ctext strong {
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
    }
    .ctext a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }

    .fg { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 13px; }
    .frow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 13px; }
    label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--slate);
    }
    input, textarea, select {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 400;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      outline: none;
      width: 100%;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
      appearance: none;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
    input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder { color: var(--slate-light); }
    input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus { border-color: var(--blue); background: var(--white); }

    textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 88px; }
    select option { background: var(--white); }

    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--navy-hover); }

    .form-note { font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate-light); text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 24px 60px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    footer img { height: 26px; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); opacity: .6; display: block; }
    .fc { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.25); font-weight: 300; }
    .fe { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
    .fe:hover { color: #7AA3F5; }

    /* Reveal animation */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
    .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      section { padding: 52px 24px; }
      nav { padding: 0 24px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .section-header, .how-grid, .why-layout, .form-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .clients-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      footer { padding: 20px 24px; }
      .hero-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 580px) {
      .services-grid, .clients-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .frow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-stats { display: none; }
    }

    /* Reduced motion */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
      .reveal { transition: none; }
      .pb { animation: none; transform: scaleY(1); }
      .hero-tag-dot { animation: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav id="navbar" aria-label="Primary navigation">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#" aria-label="FirmNest Group home">
      <img src="firmnest-logo.png" alt="FirmNest Group" />
    </a>

    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="#how">How We Work</a></li>
      <li><a href="#clients">Clients</a></li>
      <li><a href="#why">Why FirmNest</a></li>
    </ul>

    <a href="#consultation" class="nav-cta">Book Consultation</a>
  </nav>

  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-tag reveal"><span class="hero-tag-dot"></span>AI-Powered Finance Advisory</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title reveal" style="transition-delay:.08s">Finance That<br><em>Thinks Faster.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc reveal" style="transition-delay:.16s">
        FirmNest Group brings AI-powered finance and operations expertise to founder-led and growth-stage businesses.
        Structured thinking, cleaner decisions, faster outcomes.
      </p>
      <a href="#consultation" class="btn-primary reveal" style="transition-delay:.24s">Book a Consultation</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-stats reveal" style="transition-delay:.32s" aria-label="Key highlights">
      <div class="hs"><div class="hs-val">AI<span>+</span>Human</div><div class="hs-lbl">Delivery Model</div></div>
      <div class="hs"><div class="hs-val">5<span>x</span></div><div class="hs-lbl">Faster Reporting</div></div>
      <div class="hs"><div class="hs-val">£1M<span>+</span></div><div class="hs-lbl">Revenue Range</div></div>
      <div class="hs"><div class="hs-val">UK<span> Based</span></div><div class="hs-lbl">London, England</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow reveal">What We Do</div>
        <h2 class="reveal" style="transition-delay:.07s">Five Practices.<br><em>One Standard.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="lead reveal" style="transition-delay:.12s">
        Every engagement is built around a specific outcome. AI delivers faster, with more precision, at a fraction of the traditional cost.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="svc reveal">
        <div class="svc-n">01</div>
        <div class="svc-title">FP&amp;A Assistance</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">AI-assisted forecasting, scenario modelling, and board-ready reporting that gives leadership real clarity without the manual overhead.</p>
        <div class="svc-arr">&#8594;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc reveal" style="transition-delay:.07s">
        <div class="svc-n">02</div>
        <div class="svc-title">Operational Finance</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">We map your financial operations, identify what is costing you margin, and automate the workflows that should never be manual.</p>
        <div class="svc-arr">&#8594;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc reveal" style="transition-delay:.14s">
        <div class="svc-n">03</div>
        <div class="svc-title">Fundraising &amp; VC Readiness</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">Investor-grade financial models, data room preparation, and the commercial narrative that gives you the best chance in front of capital.</p>
        <div class="svc-arr">&#8594;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc reveal" style="transition-delay:.21s">
        <div class="svc-n">04</div>
        <div class="svc-title">Tax &amp; Compliance Support</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">Planning support and coordination with your qualified accountants and tax advisers so tax decisions align with your commercial reality.</p>
        <div class="svc-arr">&#8594;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc reveal" style="transition-delay:.28s">
        <div class="svc-n">05</div>
        <div class="svc-title">Founder Advisory</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">A fractional CFO and strategic finance partner for founders who need senior commercial thinking without the full-time cost.</p>
        <div class="svc-arr">&#8594;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc ai-card reveal" style="transition-delay:.35s">
        <div class="svc-n">AI+</div>
        <div class="svc-title">AI at Every Layer</div>
        <p class="svc-desc">Every service is delivered with AI-enabled speed. Faster analysis, smarter models, real-time intelligence your business can act on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how">
    <div class="eyebrow reveal">Our Approach</div>
    <h2 class="reveal" style="transition-delay:.07s">Human Expertise,<br><em>AI Speed.</em></h2>

